Waspinator flew overhead then got blown up by a laser "Why this always
happen to Waspinator?" Waspinator's head asked.

"Yeee Ha! These Tripreds have blasters" Quickstrike said barley
avoiding a laser, he then returned fire with an energy blast from his
snake head at one of the laser turrets.

Inferno was knocked out of the air but a laser but landed behind some
rocks. He recollected himself and looked down at himself, the laser
had damaged his torso but other then that he wasn't do badly damaged
"For the glory of the royalty!" he said and peaked out from behind the
rock and launched a rocket at the base.
